**🐳 What is Docker?**

**Docker** is an **open-source containerization platform** that allows you to build, package, and run applications in **lightweight, portable containers**.

&nbsp;**📦 A Container Bundles:**

- Application code
- Runtime (JVM, Python, Node, etc.)
- System libraries
- Environment variables
- Configuration

&nbsp;**❓ Why Docker?**

**⚠️ Before Docker**

- Applications depended heavily on the OS and environment
- "Works on my machine" problems were common
- Virtual Machines (VMs) were heavy and slow

